    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好参与MotoGP™25！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受2025赛季的每一个细节</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >参加官方锦标赛，化身为你最喜爱的车手，驾驶本赛季最经典的摩托车，征战经典赛道。借助虚幻引擎5的强大性能、MotoGP™ Stewards的公平竞赛保障，以及现场录制并经过全面改进的官方摩托车音效设计，体验前所未有的逼真竞赛以及绝对的刺激之感。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/4f4e83323869b5677a5d0693f3dcb9d9.poster.avif?t=1753692631\" width=620 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/4f4e83323869b5677a5d0693f3dcb9d9.webm?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/4f4e83323869b5677a5d0693f3dcb9d9.mp4?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >铸就竞赛传奇</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你成为MotoGP™ Legend的征程将从这里开始！深入探索摩托车的进化历程，在赛季中选择你的生涯Turning Point，发展赛道外社交关系，然后见证这些选择如何在周末的比赛中一步步演变发展。掌握车手转会市场动态，创造独一无二的旅程。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/c0a060306cba301f87d8848411758a03.poster.avif?t=1753692631\" width=620 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/c0a060306cba301f87d8848411758a03.webm?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/c0a060306cba301f87d8848411758a03.mp4?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >精进赛车技艺</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在生涯模式和快速模式中通过全新的Race Off竞赛项目，像冠军一样训练。驾驶Motard、Flat Track和Minibikes摩托车，在2个原创环境中的4条专用赛道上一展身手。接受激动人心的挑战，提升车手体能，解锁配件，磨练技术，主宰赛道！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/906035b552c472e4eb441ab4bcd9da29.poster.avif?t=1753692631\" width=620 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/906035b552c472e4eb441ab4bcd9da29.webm?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/906035b552c472e4eb441ab4bcd9da29.mp4?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >尽享个性化赛车体验</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >是选择极致可玩性还是全模拟挑战？通过全新的Arcade体验模式，直接投入紧张刺激的比赛中。或者在Pro体验模式中熟悉每一个赛道细节、燃料消耗和电子辅助系统，体验逼真的MotoGP™竞速！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助改良的自适应难度模式、神经辅助系统和全新的新手教程，完全掌控你的摩托车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/c57a73c80ee69884f21831e8d2b9bbbb.poster.avif?t=1753692631\" width=620 height=178 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/c57a73c80ee69884f21831e8d2b9bbbb.webm?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3077390/extras/c57a73c80ee69884f21831e8d2b9bbbb.mp4?t=1753692631\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主宰赛场</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >排位赛和全方位跨平台游玩功能可让你与实力相当的好友和对手一较高下，而不受游戏平台的限制*。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借助全套游戏内编辑器，释放创意，向世界展示你的风格。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >*Nintendo Switch除外</p>",
